help.153

	*spells <player>

This command allows a DM or caretaker to list the spells known 
by any player who is logged in.  
NOTE:  There is a *set command to cause the player to either learn
or forget a particular spell.  The command is a toggle, and the
player either learns or forgets the spell each time the flag is set.
(See the help command for more information on *set commands.)

examples:
:*spells casper
3 spells known by Casper:
Bless, fly, light
:
:*set c casper spe light
Casper forgets light.
:
:*set c casper spe heal
Casper learns heal.
 
NOTE:  Be sure to use the abbreviation spe.

